      • buildTokenTextPattern

        protected void buildTokenTextPattern()
        Builds tokenTextPattern form getFieldsToCheck(), e.g. replacing comma or spaces for separation of list items with the vertical bar used in the regex and possible added prefixes of "sy-" are removed. If getFieldsToCheck() does not contain any text, it is left to it's initial value to match any occurrence of system fields.
